Title: Re:pray
Artist: Aimer
description: lyric with original japanese transcription and hepburn transliteration with english transaltion

歩道橋　階段　雨音
hodoukyou kaidan amaoto
手を振るよ　最後の背中に
te wo furu yo saigo no senaka ni
青に変わるライトで　時が動く
ao ni kawaru raito de toki ga ugoku
傘の波　飲み込んだ　my days
kasa no nami nomikonda my days

say a little pray for you and me
\n
もう永遠を誓えない　愛を見送ろう
mou eien wo chikaenai ai wo miokurou

誰かの為に生きてゆけない　自分を許せる強さを
dareka no tame ni ikite yukenai jibun wo yuruseru tsuyosa wo
あなたに寄り添えなかったこと　悔やまずにいられる日々を
anata ni yorisoenakatta koto kuyamazu ni irareru hibi wo
祈りは雲を引き裂き　この空に希望　解き放つ
inori wa kumo wo hikisaki kono sora ni kibou tokihanatsu

我儘も　燃やしたアルバムも　去年のような明日が欲しくて
wagamama mo moyashita arubamu mo kyonen no you na ashita ga hoshikute
あなたのそのすべてを守るために　わたしを守りたかった
anata no sono subete wo mamoru tame ni watashi wo mamoritakatta

no more cry and dry your eyes
\n
もう二度と振り向かない　引き留める声もない恋
mou nidoto furimukanai hikitomeru koe mo nai koi

泣かないで　これで終わりじゃない
nakanaide kore de owari janai
ただ時が過ぎて消えただけ
tada toki ga sugite kieta dake
この胸にいま刻んだものは　包まれたぬくもりだけ
kono mune ni ima kizanda mono wa tsutsumareta nukumori dake
さよなら愛したあなた
sayonara aishita anata
さよなら愛されたわたし
sayonara aisareta watashi

恋しくて　ただ恋しくて　でも　望んでた場所はここじゃない
koishikute tada koishikute demo nozondeta basho wa koko janai
その声がまだ残ってる　でも　届けたい明日へのpray
sono koe ga mada nokotteru demo todoketai ashita e no pray

誰かの為に生きてゆけない自分を許せる強さを
dareka no tame ni ikite yukenai jibun wo yuruseru tsuyosa wo
あなたに寄り添えなかったこと悔やまずにいられる日々を
anata ni yorisoenakatta koto kuyamazu ni irareru hibi wo
祈りは雲を引き裂き　この空に希望　解き放つ
inori wa kumo wo hikisaki kono sora ni kibou tokihanatsu


Overpass, stairs, sound of rain
I wave my hand to your receding back
With lights turning to blue, time moves on
The wave of the umbrella swallowed my days

Say a little prayer for you and me
Let’s bid farewell to love that can no longer promise eternity

The strength to forgive oneself for not being able to live for someone else
Days when I can regret not being able to be by your side
Prayers tear through the clouds, releasing hope into this sky

I wanted a tomorrow like last year, burning my selfishness and albums
I wanted to protect myself to protect everything about you

No more cry and dry your eyes
Love without a voice to hold you back and look back again

Don’t cry, this is not the end
It just passed with time
What is now engraved in my heart is just the warmth that enveloped me
Goodbye, my beloved
Goodbye, I who was loved

I miss you, just miss you, but this is not the place I wished for
Your voice still lingers, but I want to send it to tomorrow

The strength to forgive oneself for not being able to live for someone else
Days when I can regret not being able to be by your side
Prayers tear through the clouds, releasing hope into this sky
